gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 127, Wizards 119
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Wizards, 127-119. Franz Wagner recorded 28 points, eight rebounds and nine assists for the Magic, while Paolo Banchero (24 points, eight assists) and Anthony Black (career-high 23 points) added a combined 47 points in the victory. Jordan Poole tallied 30 points, three assists and three steals for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Magic have won back-to-back games and improve to 18-11 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 5-24.
